    OnDownloaderCompletionListener
    Interface definition for a callback to invoked when the downloading task is finished.
    OnDownloaderErrorListener
    Interface definition of a callback to be invoked when there has been an error during an asynchronous operation (other errors will throw exceptions at method call time).
    OnDownloaderProgressUpdateListener
    Interface definition for a callback to be invoked when the download progress update.
    OnDownloaderSpeedUpdateListener
    Interface definition for a callback to be invoked to notify the current download speed.
